data.description:
LIKE NEW, SPACIOUS ONE-STORY, MOVE-IN READY, 3BDRM/2BA, 1,725 SF Belmont Model in SWEETWATER BY DEL WEBB-- Jacksonville's Premier 55+ Active Adult Community! MORE THAN $36K OF SELLER'S UPGRADES & QUALITY IMPROVEMENTS! NEW ROOF 2023. A.O. SMITH WATER HEATER 2022. Interior features incl: a spacious ceramic tiled foyer, open Great Room & adjoining Dining Room w/wainscoting, NEW neutral SHERMAN-WILLIAMS designer wall color & NEW carpet & upgraded pad throughout that will go with any Buyer's decor, lighting & fans. Fully equipped Gourmet kitchen w/warm 42'' cabinetry, Corian countertops, NEW Delta Charmaine Single Handle Pull-Down Kitchen Faucet, Breakfast nook w/ upgraded 18'' ceramic flooring, & ALL NEW GE Stainless Fingerprint Resistant Appliances. All appliances convey incl. washer/dryer. Sellers Exceptional Upgrades & Improvements

Upgrades and Improvements Completed in 2023
" Roof - GAF Lifetime Architectural Shingle w/Silver Pledge Warranty
" GE Refrigerator - Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel
" GE Range - w/Convection & Air Fry Cooking
" GE Dishwasher - Quieter Model w/Bottle Washer
" GE Over-the-Range Microwave
" New Carpet & Upgraded Pad Throughout
" Fresh Sherwin-Williams Interior Paint Throughout
" Cool Deck Front Patio & Lanai Paint
" 2" Faux Wood Blinds
" Ultra Quiet Genie Garage Door Opener with 2 remotes
" New Lanai Screen & Door Hardware
" Hunter Autero 52" Ceiling Fan in Living Room
" Delta Charmain Single Handle Pull-Down Sprayer Kitchen Faucet
" Kohler Stonewood Elongated Toilet Seats
" Landscape Improvements

Other Outstanding Home Features
" Plantation Shutters in Front Facing Windows
" Screen Enclosed Lanai w/Pull Down Shades
" Ceramic Tile Flooring in Entry, Kitchen, & Bathrooms
" Fingerprint Resistant Stainless-Steel Appliances
" Paver Driveway & Walkway
" Professional Landscaping
" Transferable Termite Bond w/Massey Services, Inc.
" Lawn Spraying Maintenance w/Turf Science
" Ceiling Fans in All Bedrooms, Office, & Living Room
" Hurricane Shutters
" Separate Irrigation Meter
" Lennox HVAC System (2017) w/Air Engineers Service Contract
" A. O. Smith 100 Gallon Water Heater (2022)
" All Home Systems Serviced
" No CDD Fees

Other exceptional features: Quality Concrete Block Construction, Designer Paver Driveway & Walkway, Very Reasonable HOA Fees that include World Class 55+ Amenities, Onsite Property Management, Onsite Lifestyle Director, and NO CDD fees! Sweetwater is centrally located to major shopping (St. John's Town Center), grocery stores, restaurants, pharmacies, major medical (Mayo Clinic & Urgent Care), & easy access to major highways, the airport, or the beaches.

SWEETWATER residents enjoy the fabulous 22,000 SF Amenities Center called Summerland Hall, w/State-of-the-Art Fitness Center, Indoor heated & Outdoor Pools, indoor Jacuzzi, Ballroom & Dance Floor, Game & Crafts Rooms, Library, Business Center, Yoga/Pilates Room, Billiards Room, -- all staffed by a full-time Lifestyle Director. Tennis courts, bocce ball courts, outdoor pavilion for picnicking, lighted walking/nature trails, bike lanes, & more!

Welcome home to the Sweet Life of Sweetwater at 11285 Water Spring Circle!
